// Ionic water analysis as flowsheet components: water + the seven master
// ions of the brackish analysis (case-local constant/components/*.dat,
// MW from the electrolyte catalogue).  Activity/EoS models are not
// consulted by the membrane transport (dilute aqueous, van't Hoff
// osmotic model); `ideal` keeps the loader happy.  The SCALING audit
// uses the electrolyte speciation kernel (Davies) instead -- see
// constant/electrolyte/.
components       ( water  Ca  Mg  Na  K  Cl  SO4  HCO3 );

activityModel    { model  ideal; }
equationOfState  { model  idealGas; }
